description:
This fine garment is made of black silk interwoven with faint, silvery threads. While wearing it, you gain the following benefits.
{"type": "entries", "name": "Poison Resistance", "entries": ["You have {@variantrule Resistance|XPHB} to Poison damage."]}
{"type": "entries", "name": "Spider Climb", "entries": ["You have a {@variantrule Climb Speed|XPHB} equal to your {@variantrule Speed|XPHB} and can move up, down, and across vertical surfaces and along ceilings, while leaving your hands free."]}
